Shadowhunters -LRB- also known as Shadowhunters : The Mortal Instruments -RRB- is an American fantasy television series that is loosely based on The Mortal Instruments by Cassandra Clare , and developed for television by Ed Decter .
It is the second adaptation of the novel series , after the 2013 film The Mortal Instruments : City of Bones , which like Shadowhunters was produced by Constantin Film .
The show received a straight-to-series order on March 30 , 2015 , and premiered on January 12 , 2016 on Freeform .
In March 2016 , it was announced that the series had been renewed for a second season of 20 episodes , which premiered on January 2 , 2017 .
In April 2017 , it was announced that the series had been renewed for a third season of 20 episodes .